description: This repository implements a hybrid computational framework for simulating shock waves in non-ideal gases. It integrates extended RankineHugoniot models (using PengRobinson and RedlichKwong EOS), high-fidelity FVM/FDM simulations with adaptive mesh refinement, and machine learning for rapid predictions. Case studies include Real Gases

A machine learning framework for real-time gravitational wave (GW) signal classification using 1D-CNN and ResNet architectures.
